param _name Fund name
param _fundOwner Fund owner
param _investment Initial investment committed
param _feeRate Annual fee rate

Invest(uint256,uint256).details: Allows an investor to commit an amount of virtual capital to the fund dev Also takes care of fee payment up front param _fundNum Fund number param _investment Virtual capital committed dev Uses stopInEmergency() modifier

checkFee(uint256).details: Checks whether a payment is due and how much param  _fundNun Fund number return payment uint that returns the payment due return paymentDue bool that represents whether a payment is due

checkFeeRate(uint256).details: Passes arguments to checkFeeRate() in Misc.sol param _fundNum Fund Number return uint Fee Rate

closeFund(uint256).details: Allows manager to shut down a fund's operations param  _fundNum Fund Number dev Uses isOwner() and stopInEmergency modifiers

collectFees(uint256).details: Owner of fund collects fees from smart contract param _fundNum FundNumber

constructor.details: Constructor for the contract dev sets the admin variable equal to the address that initialized the contract

endFundraising(uint256).details: Allows manager to end the fundraising period param _fundNum Fund number dev Uses isOwner() and stopinEmergency() modifiers

getFundDetails(uint256).details: Get non-user specific fund Information param _fundNum Fund number return bytes32 Fund name return address Fund owner return uint Total Capital return uint Capital Deployed return uint Fee Rate return uint Payment Cycle

getFundDetails2(uint256,address).details: Get user specific fund information param _fundNum Fund number param _addr Address of interest return bool Investor Status return uint Virtual balance return uint Fees in Escrow

getIpfsHash(uint256).return: ipfsHash 32-byte hexadecimal representation of ipfsHash digesthash_function type of hash_function used for encodingsize of the length of the digest

initializeFund(bytes32,address,uint256,u.details: Initializes a fund with the given arguments and stores it in a Fund Struct within a Data Struct param _name Fund name param _fundOwner Fund owner param _investment Initial investment committed param _feeRate Annual fee rate param _paymentCycle Payment Cycle (in days) param _ipfsHash Digest of ipfs hash param _hash_function Hash function of ipfs hash param _size size of ipfs hash dev uses stopInEmergency() modifier dev lifetimeCount is used in InitLib.initializeFund because current implementation makes it difficult to delete and replace fund data

payFee(uint256).details: One-time pay fee function param _fundNum Fund number dev Uses stopInEmergency modifier

placeOrder(uint256,bytes32,bytes32,uint2.details: Takes order information and passes it to OrderLib.placeOrder() for error checking param _fundNum Fund number param _action Type of order: buy or sell param _ticker String representation of stock ticker param _qty Quantity of shares param _price Price per share in wei dev Uses stopInEmergency modifier dev Emits OrderPlaced event

withdrawFunds(uint256,uint256).details: Allows an investor to withdraw virtual balance and unearned fees param _fundNum Fund Number param _amound Amount to be withdrawn
